Maxima only looked at him without emotion. Then turned to Blackstorm to wait 
for her. "Hydras has a special mission for Blackstorm. & that is all. For the 
moment, remain here. I will return to escort you to hydras once I am finished 
with Blackstorm's briefing."

Somehow, she had a feeling that Hevn wouldn't listen to her command. 

--part1_125.236739a9.2c2fbfd8_boundary
